      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get what you're saying but it feels so temporary. like, why bother making these memories or building these connections when it's all just going to be incinerated or underwater in a few decades? it feels like we're just prolonging the inevitable pain. it's not even about being optimistic anymore, it's just... everything feels so hollow and pointless.",
